data.description: Check out this little gem!  With only 610 square feet, this cabin is super cute and packs a big punch!  Sitting on nearly an acre surrounded by trees and nature, this home is a treasure.  Gated entry at driveway provides security and curb appeal.  Front porch is large and super welcoming.  Enjoy an outdoor living room and/or dining while you listen to the rain, watch the birds, or stargaze.  Living room has propane gas log fireplace that also provides heat.  Living room has pine wood floors.  Kitchen has granite countertops, stackable washer and dryer, dishwasher, microwave, and refrigerator on one wall--very functional.  Bedroom is good-sized with walk-in closet.  Flooring in bedroom is not attached so it's easily removed if you prefer the wood.  Bathroom has tile shower, granite countertop sink, and opens to the living room or bedroom.  Carport, nice storage building, lots of privacy.  This sweet cabin is going to go quickly, so hurry to make it your home sweet home today!
